{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act26side", "eventName": "空想花庭", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HE-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "在花園裡", "storyInfo": "沉默的聖徒拾起那枝花莖斷折，花瓣焚毀的花。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g2_abandonsancturay", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.8, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$dignified_intro", "key": "$dignified_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快來看這個，霍斯特！這邊，你看！", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "居然真在聖像前種上花了，而且總覺得這裡的花開得比其他地方更漂亮哦？克萊芒那傢伙脾氣雖然軟了點，但還是有點本領的嘛！", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真虧斯特凡諾能同意，又是挖聖堂地板，又是到處找土什麼的......連用什麼土都這麼講究。", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "慢點跑，別忘記你身上還有傷。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這點小傷算什麼？", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小傷也有惡化的風險。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，現在別再叫那個名字了，叫我杰拉爾德。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了好了，知道了！你怎麼也開始管東管西了......可別和斯特凡諾學這個啊！", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯特凡諾那老頭子就是管得太多，所以才長那麼多皺紋。", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老人家就得放寬心，少操心少管事，這樣才能長壽！", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛琳！說得太過了，斯特凡諾只是一心為修道院的將來打算。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們能像現在這樣住下，也多虧了他。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道！我只是說他打算得太多了，我看了都替他覺得累得慌！", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就怕他哪天扛不住了，受不了了，那是要吃大苦頭的......！", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯特凡諾不會聽勸，他在薩科塔里應該也是特別固執的那一類，只要是他認準了的道理，就一定會堅持到底。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我們能在這裡定居下來，也多虧了他的這一點。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說我們薩卡茲和其他人沒什麼不同......", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老頭子這話說得沒錯啊。", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，要是真有他扛不住了的那天，大不了你我幫忙搭把手，替他撐著......也算是報恩了。", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也別再想之前的事了。我們那時離開卡茲戴爾，已經背棄了特蕾西婭殿下......杰拉爾德，我們回不了頭了。", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你我都是。", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我知道。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用這樣提醒我，愛琳。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾追隨殿下，但不知道什麼時候起，我不再能看見殿下描繪的圖景......在卡茲戴爾的兩位殿下身上，我找不到我們薩卡茲的未來。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別難過。", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒事。至少現在，我們已經有了新的生活。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我把願意離開的人帶出卡茲戴爾，就會對他們負起責任。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在這日子......比從前好多了。", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別大意，我們現在和從前不同，沒有物資支援，那些強盜裡偶爾也有不好對付的。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是不是也太小心了一點？", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "搞不好幾年、十幾年之後，凶名赫赫的雇傭兵都要變成鄉下獵戶囉。哈哈哈哈！", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈哈......", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那個，我說，杰拉爾德啊。", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想過你真的放下武器，變成鄉下獵戶會是什麼樣嗎？", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到時候我又會變成什麼樣？", "name": "愛琳"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有。我沒想過。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時候的我會變成什麼樣......", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛琳，如果你願意，你可以親自確認。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很久以前，在與人拼殺後的深夜，杰拉爾德總會在想要喘口氣時放任自己抬頭看天。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天空是壓抑的黑色，篝火漸熄，火焰逐漸冷卻。"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰場上渾身染血的雇傭兵擦掉身上臉上的髒汙，注視著同樣傷痕累累的同伴，短暫地思考過某些對於他們來說有些奢侈的問題。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們這樣的薩卡茲，是否真的能夠擁有所謂幸福的一生？"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他曾堅信薩卡茲重新擁有家的那天一定會來，只是他感到越來越無力，越來越力不從心。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們流了太多血。在實現那位殿下的美好願景前，他們的血就快要流盡了。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "杰拉爾德終於決定放下卡茲戴爾的一切，他帶上那些快要活不下去的人，逃一樣地離開了曾經為之拼命的土地。"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們隱姓埋名，終於找到一處能容他們薩卡茲安身的場所，他們只期盼在這裡過上平靜的、與常人無異的生活。"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個願望一度得以實現。"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是到底是從什麼時候開始，生活開始變得苦澀，開始無法呼吸？"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就好像是放在台子上無人品嘗的佳餚。"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明努力維持，沒人破壞，卻還是變了質。"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果只有鮮血能讓這一切結束......"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼我所能做的事，就只剩下這麼一件。"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutryinside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒，你不必再勸我。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#10$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能走，也走不了。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#10$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從沒告訴過你我之前的名字，那不是什麼值得回味的過去，不過是個喪家之犬，一個臭名昭著的逃兵。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#10$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有我在，他們就有理由對其他人動手。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#10$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這副表情，我只是先一步去見愛琳，這沒什麼，死亡對我這樣曾經刀口舔血的人來說並不算太陌生。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#8$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果用我的腦袋就能交換其他人的生路，也算是值得。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#8$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我走之後，你不用擔心這裡剩下的人，他們會聽我的話。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#8$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊蒙德還年輕，恐怕他會有點衝動。到時候......就拜託你多勸勸。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#7$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後......", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫我轉告斯特凡諾，或許最開始我們在荒野上流浪那會，就不該貿然停下，不該嘗試留下來。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#4$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是對我，對我們薩卡茲來說，這裡實在太好了......", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#4$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能一起生活這麼多年，一切真像是一場夢，但我清楚我們終究要面對現實。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#4$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "替我向斯特凡諾說一句——謝謝，我很抱歉。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#4$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來就拜託你了，克萊芒。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#4$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_926_1#4$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到了最後，還是以這個身份......", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#4$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我究竟是個獵戶，還是......依然是那個雇傭兵？", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#4$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，愛琳，我現在的樣子，恐怕你看了也不會感到滿意吧。", "name": "杰拉爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_926_1#4$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g3_abandonsancturay_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......天亮了。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從昨天到今天，好像發生了很多事。但又好像只是一眨眼，一切就都結束了。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管怎麼說......這個夜晚確實漫長，不是嗎？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在做什麼？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是什麼值得您過問的事，費德里科先生。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想找一朵花，杰拉爾德總不能空著手去見愛琳，這不太好。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我好像......昨晚的那場大火把東西都燒沒了，什麼都沒剩下。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你只是想要鮮花，不必特地來這裡。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不清楚，費德里科先生，那不一樣。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的花是特別的。它們是這座修道院培育出來的特殊品種......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "象徵友誼與希望。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，友誼與希望。主教閣下曾告訴我，這是拉特蘭與伊比利亞攜手合作的象徵，是修道院最重要的東西之一......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多好啊......當時的我，立刻就被它們迷住了。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個時候修道院裡還到處都是成片種植的花卉，每到花期，從鐘塔那樣的高處往下看，整座修道院就像是被花填滿。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛琳特別喜歡那種風景，杰拉爾德也喜歡......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有很多人原本很怕薩卡茲，不敢和他們說話，但在經過一次花期後，彼此之間的關係就變好了很多。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家發現，原來就算是傳聞中冷酷好鬥的薩卡茲，也會在路過花圃時，停下步子看一小會，也會嘗試摘一兩朵，裝飾在家中。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們看起來一點也不像是什麼凶惡的亡命之徒，他們和我們沒什麼不同......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡還有一朵。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？啊......您說的是聖像下面的這一朵嗎？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到它了，它很幸運，應該是正好被倒下的聖像壓住，才能像這樣保存下來......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是很可惜，它不是我想要的那一朵。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "理由？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您看這朵花......看看它，難道您還不明白嗎？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算躲藏在聖像之下得以倖存，它的花莖卻早已折斷，花瓣也被火焰燎烤，它已經傷痕累累了。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但它還在。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎，它真的還在嗎？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我之前也相信，有些東西可以扛過風吹日曬，不怕刀山火海。請不要笑話我......我曾經真心相信過。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個時候，儘管生活依然不算輕鬆，但一切好像都還很好。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要有一點餘裕，妮娜大嬸就會給孩子們做些小點心。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您聽過青草格子餅嗎？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "妮娜大嬸和赫曼一起，用從拉特蘭帶來的配方，加上薩卡茲栽培的香草，做出了大家都喜歡的、獨屬於修道院的甜點。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "妮娜大嬸總是說，我們大人苦一點沒什麼，可是我們的孩子們，他們不能只知道“苦”的滋味。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子們需要知道什麼是“甜”......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我會記住這種甜點。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，不重要了，我們已經忘記甜味太久......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事到如今，恐怕已經沒有人會特地再去做一份格子餅了。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科先生，有的時候我會感到好奇。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果薩科塔沒有那麼特殊，如果拉特蘭都是如我一樣，最平凡、最普通、最不值一提的人......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那座聖城，還會是如今這般模樣嗎？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭，還會是拉特蘭嗎？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#10$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不知道。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真遺憾。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒，你......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你已經不再相信——你已經改變想法了嗎？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是不得不看到現實。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "許多東西並沒有人們想的那樣牢不可破，考驗只會讓它受傷。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而只要有了一點瑕疵，混入了一丁點異物，哪怕只是有一點不起眼的傷痕，都再也沒法修復，沒法挽回......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像您發現的那朵花，費德里科先生。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡已經沒有我想要的花了。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快要到晨會的時間了，我也該走了。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再見，費德里科先生。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "39_i08", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 100.0, "yFrom": 50.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 15.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科·吉亞洛獨自留在這個清晨的聖堂。"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火災留下的痕跡已經過簡單處理，失去了原有擺設的聖堂內越來越空曠，只有腳步聲獨自迴盪。"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科是一位優秀的公證所執行者，這是他成為執行者的第六年，工作早已得心應手。"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同時，這也是他被加上聖徒名號的第一個年頭，沒有人能給他啟發或指點。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉默的聖徒拾起那枝花莖斷折，花瓣焚毀的花。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖像給予其庇護，讓其免於被火焰吞噬，在那樣的大火中，它的倖存是某種奇蹟。"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可在另一個人眼中，這份奇蹟一文不值。"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "花還在。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卻不是想要的那一朵？", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不可修復的傷痕......", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無法理解。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭是否還會是拉特蘭......？", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "............", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可參考的資料不足，無法得出答案。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行者費德里科在這時忽然意識到——"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒的神色實在是太過平靜了。"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他既沒有提起杰拉爾德的死，也沒有提起其他薩卡茲的安排。"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而自己呢？"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不伴隨行動的言語毫無力量，所以他不會說一定會找出真相。"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不會說，自己一定會完成杰拉爾德最後的請求。"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科注視著眼前殘破的花。"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他有所預感——"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總有一天，自己所懷有的疑問，能夠在這朵花上得到解答。"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutryinside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯——哈噢唔——", "name": "艾倫戴爾"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早上啦......薩拉，該起床啦......", "name": "艾倫戴爾"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，唔呣唔呣，呼......", "name": "艾倫戴爾"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_929_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾倫，艾倫！醒一醒，艾倫——", "name": "艾絲塔拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_929_1#8$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別睡啦，媽媽，媽媽昨天回來啦！", "name": "艾絲塔拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_929_1#8$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_929_1#8$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_928_1#4$1", "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_928_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？！", "name": "艾倫戴爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_928_1#4$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽回來了嗎？在哪裡在哪裡？", "name": "艾倫戴爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_928_1#4$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_929_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯！一定是媽媽，你看——", "name": "艾絲塔拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_929_1#8$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_928_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇！這是媽媽給我們的新毯子嗎？但是破破的......", "name": "艾倫戴爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_928_1#4$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_928_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過上面還有圈圈的圖案呢！還有長翅膀的小人......嗯，沒錯，這是媽媽之前說會給我們帶的！", "name": "艾倫戴爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_928_1#3$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_929_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "破一點也沒關係呀，我們是好孩子，要體諒媽媽啦，媽媽自己的衣服都破破的......", "name": "艾絲塔拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_929_1#3$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_928_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦，我當然知道嘛。", "name": "艾倫戴爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_928_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，我們去找費德里科哥哥！", "name": "艾倫戴爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_928_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_929_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天也能和費德里科哥哥一起玩嗎......？", "name": "艾絲塔拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_929_1#8$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_928_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "笨笨，我們是要去告訴費德里科哥哥，媽媽晚上有回來看我們，讓費德里科哥哥不要擔心啦~", "name": "艾倫戴爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_928_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}